    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, or swirl marks, reflecting the care this car has received throughout its life. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces, lights, and glass are in flawless shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new: the upholstery shows no signs of wear, fading, or staining, and all controls, displays, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. This is a car that has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide its next owner with a truly premium ownership experience from day one.",
      "price": 47500.0,
