    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal on a Project Car \u2014 Great for the Budget-Conscious Buyer! \ud83d\udd27 Looking for an affordable vehicle that won't break the bank? This car is priced to reflect its true condition \u2014 it shows its age with noticeable wear inside and out, and will likely need some mechanical attention to get it running at its best. That said, it's a real opportunity for a handy DIYer, a first-time wrench-turner, or anyone who just needs basic transportation and is comfortable with a fixer-upper. No smoke and mirrors here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly! Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you. \ud83d\ude97",
      "price": 5500.0,
