    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. This is a truly exceptional used car that presents and performs like new in virtually every respect. The exterior is flawless: the paint retains a deep, rich gloss with no visible scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, moldings, and glass are in perfect condition. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, carpets, headliner, and all surfaces show no meaningful wear, staining, or fading. All electronics, controls, and infotainment features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with smooth, confident power. Service history is up to date, and there are no known mechanical issues. The tires have substantial tread remaining, and brakes are in excellent shape. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that requires absolutely nothing \u2014 you can drive it home and enjoy it from day one without a single concern.",
      "price": 46000.0,
